    <item>
      <title>拜登将出席特朗普就职典礼 力图恢复权力和平过渡传统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/biden-to-attend-trump-inauguration-in-bid-to-restore-transition-traditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，他决心在本月晚些时候和平移交权力，同时警告不要淡化四年前为阻止其选举认证而发生的暴徒袭击美国国会大厦的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/biden-to-attend-trump-inauguration-in-bid-to-restore-transition-traditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 04:47:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾称中国船只破坏海底电缆 涉嫌蓄意破坏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/taiwan-says-chinese-ship-broke-subsea-cable-in-alleged-sabotage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾怀疑一艘中国大陆货船周五损坏了其东北海岸附近的一条海底电缆，这一涉嫌破坏行为凸显了台北海上通信基础设施的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/taiwan-says-chinese-ship-broke-subsea-cable-in-alleged-sabotage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 04:16:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国通胀率七个月来首次回到目标水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/thai-inflation-returns-to-target-for-first-time-in-seven-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国通胀率七个月来首次回到央行的目标区间，在全球不确定性加剧的情况下，货币当局有能力抵御政府进一步降息的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/thai-inflation-returns-to-target-for-first-time-in-seven-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 04:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国引诱台湾人移居台北引发担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-enticing-taiwanese-to-live-there-stirs-concern-in-taipei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾一位高级官员称，中国为吸引更多台湾人获得在大陆居住和工作的许可所做的努力，引发了台北方面的担忧，他们担心北京方面可能正在为干涉该自治岛屿的事务做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/china-enticing-taiwanese-to-live-there-stirs-concern-in-taipei</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:57:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚法院允许纳吉布就 1MDB 罪行申请软禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/former-malaysia-leader-najib-steps-up-campaign-for-house-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚法院允许前总理纳吉布拉扎克 (Najib Razak) 提出申请，在家中服完因与问题财富基金 1MDB 相关的罪行所判处的剩余刑期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/former-malaysia-leader-najib-steps-up-campaign-for-house-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:54:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将允许更多人道主义援助流入叙利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-set-to-allow-for-more-humanitarian-aid-to-flow-to-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，拜登政府将在叙利亚总统巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后向叙利亚提供有限的制裁救济，以增加人道主义援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-set-to-allow-for-more-humanitarian-aid-to-flow-to-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:46:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯称对韩国代理领导能力充满信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/blinken-expresses-confidence-in-south-korea-s-acting-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯对韩国代理领导人表示有信心。在首尔努力恢复政治稳定之际，面对朝鲜不断提出的挑战，两国重申了安全联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/blinken-expresses-confidence-in-south-korea-s-acting-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:40:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯访问首尔之际朝鲜发射弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/north-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-japan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯访问韩国重申华盛顿和首尔之间的安全联盟之际，朝鲜周一发射了一枚弹道导弹，加剧了该地区的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/north-korea-launches-suspected-ballistic-missile-japan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《环球报》称加拿大总理特鲁多可能于本周辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/canada-s-trudeau-is-likely-to-resign-this-week-globe-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《环球邮报》报道，贾斯汀·特鲁多预计将于本周宣布辞去加拿大自由党领袖职务，此举将引发继任总理的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/canada-s-trudeau-is-likely-to-resign-this-week-globe-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 01:47:05 GMT</pubDate>
